Chelle's 50's Car Hop Diner

All Day Event

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


If you want to relive the 50's,Chelle's 50's Diner and Car Hop is for you. Located in Stafford, Connecticut, Chelle's is decorated with pictures of Elvis, Stafford from the
50's and guitars.

See club website at www.newenglandthunder.com for all club info, rides, membership and photo gallery
